<p><i>Summary 
</i></p>
<p> The present report is the High Commissioner&#8217;s fifth periodic report on the human 
rights situation in the Occupied Palestinian Territory submitted in the light of Human 
Rights Council resolutions S-9/1 and S-12/1. 
</p>
<p> 
 
</p>
<p>  
 * Late submission. 
</p>
